Acceptance Criteria

GIVEN the allocation process is completed and signed
THEN a final confirmation screen is displayed

AND the screen includes a global success confirmation message

IF one or more allocated equipments are managed in HAM
THEN they are listed under a "No action required" section

IF one or more allocated equipments are not managed in HAM
THEN they are listed under a "Follow-up required" section

AND the screen clearly explains that an incident has been created

AND equipment identifiers are displayed for traceability

IF an incident reference exists
THEN it is displayed next to the relevant equipment


